Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體動不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快動，快動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近東西容易發霉潮濕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想來個大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是電燈泡快要壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒辦法打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了換燈泡\N我找來了各種東西墊腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還是碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會叫我來幫忙換
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是從門下面\N流出的黑色液體…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我搬桌子的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心打翻了水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我有上去找本須和幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看起來好像很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:09:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電燈泡、桌子、水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼會有104號房？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來一樓本來有四間房間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁是103號房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我搬來時做了一點改裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺的是102號房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被搞得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不害怕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王終於登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼強嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看雜誌和網路上的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看過有人打倒過他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過這裡就可以到下個城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想不開了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打不贏那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chorizo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時ちぃ明明沒有經驗值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻打倒了遊戲裡的大魔王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和也不可能會寫這種程式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道她真的不是普通的電腦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個妳有看到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹看到海豚的“嘩啦”\N會很高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不會游泳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從表面看來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒進水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思議的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會進水，然後會很難修復
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的相關記憶資料到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我們果然還是\N有點資料不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找新保幫忙看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過新保少爺他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出門了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很睏的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時會早到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她從來沒遲到過的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個聲音，你是新保對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老師私奔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很久沒有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連話都說不上兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了門鍊就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都沒影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎樣都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在說這麼傷心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻沒有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其實很想哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少讓她在遇到\N不愉快或傷心的事時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠哭個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，為什麼要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道只剩這個方法了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許就如同你所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是我的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得不相信男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她認為就算一開始說喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出現像電腦那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會完全改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像從沒喜歡過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定私奔到深山的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣濕答答的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩愛愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說，這算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子點頭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉再幫我保管一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫你保管當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜囉，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過或許我可以幫上什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像電腦那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，讓我幫您泡杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是休息一下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我這並不是累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我當時分析ちぃ沒失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不需要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假使這孩子學會了說話\N學會了做各種不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縱使她再怎麼乖巧\N再怎麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勸你還是別喜歡上她比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想在日後\N傷心流淚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口味…不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是用跟姊姊同樣的方法泡的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝
